  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 91.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was day and night with no end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that time, there was Oberscharfuhrer [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He took over from Foss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Foss wasn't good enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he, he was-- he was the guy who liquidated the first commander in 1942, which I told you they, they, they-- they, they, they, finished one commander in '42 before I came there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the same one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- he was-- he was-- there's no words to, to, to explain what he was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So as he had the experience from bunkers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As the transports came in so heavy, I was in Crematorium 5.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And outside, there was maybe a few hundred feet-- a hundred, 200 feet-- where the electric things-- the, the, the guards were there so they dig their-- dig bunkers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Beside the ovens, they dig the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he oversaw that, how to build it, and he gave the plans and, oh, it should run down from one side to the other.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then if, if, if they-- if they burned just the corpses, then they took the fat and, and, and, and put-- and, and fired on top of the-- of the-- of the-- of the bodies in order to burn better.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he established also a, a big-- a bit platform where they took out the, the, the, the bones and they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] turned into dust, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they brought it to, to the-- to the river, to the Vistula there, the Vistula",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "near Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] at that time [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] it came-- it came in the-- in the-- in the-- trans-- in the hundreds of thousands.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the crematories were full.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
